105	[Pull-back along composition]
106	  \label{thm:Scheme_Pic_pullback_comp}
107	  \lean{AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Pic.pullback_comp}
108	  For composable scheme morphisms $f \colon X \to Y$ and $g \colon Y \to Z$,
109	  $\mathrm{Pic.pullback}\,(g \circ f) = \mathrm{Pic.pullback}\,f \circ \mathrm{Pic.pullback}\,g$.
